#offensive word

Detecting Offensive Tweets via Topical Feature Discovery over a Large Scale Twitter Corpus (Page 2)

A key observation on vulgar language is that vulgarity
is a type of linguistic style (Martin and White,
2005) that is expressed within a sentence with a certain
rhythm or periodicity, which indicates a tendency
for a piece of vulgar text to contain more
than one vulgar word


